profile: We are a professional tree care & horticultural based company grounded in safety, meticulous work and specializing in fine arboriculture services. Our services include tree pruning, removal, hedge trimming, planting, horticulture and branch collection. Serving Durham Region, Kawartha Lakes and Haliburton County is a pleasure for us. If you are not sure if we serve your area feel free to contact us or go to our website. We give only the absolute finest care to our clients. We are rooted in family, and care so much about yours.
